metadata.name: The Pepe Knight
metadata.description:
Pepe x Joker

Here we shows The Pepe Joker walking out of the hospital as some bombs explode along with his handsome Pepe folks. 
This scene is Inspired by the famous Hospital Blasting scene from The Dark Knight. 

Illustration : Sachin Rajeev
Dimensions : 3840 x 2500 pixels
Software : Adobe Photoshop
